Harbor 78, Trade Tech 71 -- Despite a 15-point halftime advantage, the Los 
Angeles Harbor College basketball team had to endure a fierce rally by the 
visiting Los Angeles Trade Tech Beavers to post a 78-71 victory. 
</P>
<P>
