<P>
La Quinta 62, Santiago 25 -- Amy Jalewalia had 23 points and 14 rebounds to 
lead La Quinta (11-3, 4-0) at Santiago. Tanya Krill had 16 points and 8 
rebounds for La Quinta. 
</P>
</TEXT>
