<HEADLINE>
<P>
FEELING USED 
</P>
</HEADLINE>
<BYLINE>
<P>
By Clipboard researched by Dallas Jamison / Los Angeles Times; Graphics by 
Doris Shields / Los Angeles Times 
</P>
</BYLINE>
<TEXT>
<P>
USED-CAR MARKET 
</P>
<P>
Who buys used cars in Orange County? Lots of people, evidently. Men are more 
likely than women to have done so, as are young people and those whose formal 
education stopped at high school. Household income, however, provides no 
differential. 
</P>
